Quickstrike:




Quickstrike was getting frustrated. No one was acknowledged him when 
he arrived. This base had to be the location where Black Arachnia 
told him to go. 

He looked around with a glower. A thought came to his mind that 
something was wrong. The gang of Predacons that came here could have 
been ambushed. Perhaps by Megatron. Or Hell Beast.

That didn't settle him any more. He hated Hell Beast more than he did 
Megatron. 

He groaned and took off to the side of the ship. He had to find a way 
in, even if it meant breaking in.
